You are an implementer subagent. Create the DailyReportAiEmailJob and register it in Kernel.php.

## Context

This is an OA system. We need a scheduled job that runs every minute, checks for AI daily report email tasks whose send_time matches current time and send_cycle matches current day, pulls daily report data, and sends email via oa-core with `ai_analysis_config` so oa-core does AI analysis before sending the email.

## Key patterns from existing DailyReportJob

Looking at the existing `DailyReportJob.php`:
- Extends `App\Jobs\MyJob`
- Uses `MailConfig::where('type', 'like', '%daily_report_%')` to find email configs
- Uses `DailyReportService::getOthersDailyReportListEnable()` to get reports
- Uses `EncryptService::app()->markEncrString()` to encrypt content
- Uses `sendEmail()` helper which calls `CoreApiLib::sendRequest('master-api/mail/send-decr', $params)`

**Important:** The `sendEmail()` function does NOT support `ai_analysis_config`. So in this Job, we need to build the params manually (like `getEmailParams` does) and add `ai_analysis_config`, then call `CoreApiLib::sendRequest('master-api/mail/send-decr', $params)` directly.

The `getEmailParams` function builds this structure:
```php
$params = [
    'decrypt_config' => [
        'obj' => '$this',
        'decrypt_columns' => $decryptColumns,
        'partly_decrypt_columns' => array_diff(['content', 'subject'], $decryptColumns),
    ],
    'receivers' => [['type' => 'token', 'tokens' => [$sfuser_token], 'filter' => 'emails', 'filter_map' => ['emails' => $toEmails]]],
    'content' => $content,
    'subject' => $subject,
];
```

We add `'ai_analysis_config' => ['system_prompt' => $task->system_prompt]` to the params.

## Files to create/modify

### 1. Create `D:\project\info-gitlab\oa\oa-server\app\Jobs\Notification\DailyReportAiEmailJob.php`

```php
<?php

namespace App\Jobs\Notification;

use App\Jobs\MyJob;
use App\Models\MailConfig;
use App\Service\DailyReportService;
use App\Service\EncryptService;
use App\Support\CoreApiLib;
use Illuminate\Support\Arr;
use Illuminate\Support\Facades\DB;

class DailyReportAiEmailJob extends MyJob
{
    public function handle(): bool
    {
        $now = now();
        $currentTime = $now->format('H:i');
        $currentDayOfWeek = $now->dayOfWeekIso; // 1=Monday, 7=Sunday
        $currentDayOfMonth = $now->day;

        $tasks = DB::table('daily_report_ai_email_tasks')
            ->where('is_on', 1)
            ->whereNull('deleted_at')
            ->where('send_time', $currentTime)
            ->get();

        if ($tasks->isEmpty()) {
            return true;
        }

        foreach ($tasks as $task) {
            if (!$this->shouldSendNow($task->send_cycle, $currentDayOfWeek, $currentDayOfMonth)) {
                continue;
            }

            try {
                $this->processTask($task);
            } catch (\Throwable $e) {
                info("[DailyReportAiEmailJob] task={$task->id} failed: {$e->getMessage()}" . $e->getTraceAsString());
            }
        }

        info('[DailyReportAiEmailJob] finished');
        return true;
    }

    private function shouldSendNow(string $sendCycle, int $dayOfWeek, int $dayOfMonth): bool
    {
        return match ($sendCycle) {
            'daily' => true,
            'weekly_monday' => $dayOfWeek === 1,
            'weekly_friday' => $dayOfWeek === 5,
            'monthly_first' => $dayOfMonth === 1,
            default => false,
        };
    }

    private function processTask(object $task): void
    {
        $sfuserId = $task->sfuser_id;

        // 读取邮箱配置
        $mc = MailConfig::where('type', "daily_report_{$sfuserId}")->first();
        if (!$mc || empty(Arr::get($mc->config, 'to_email'))) {
            info("[DailyReportAiEmailJob] task={$task->id} no email config, skip");
            return;
        }

        $toEmails = Arr::get($mc->config, 'to_email');
        $sfuserToken = Arr::get($mc->config, 'sfuser_authorized_token', '');
        if (!$sfuserToken) {
            info("[DailyReportAiEmailJob] task={$task->id} no sfuser_token, skip");
            return;
        }

        // 确定日报日期范围
        [$startDate, $endDate] = $this->getDateRange($task->report_range);

        // 拉取日报数据
        $dailyService = app(DailyReportService::class);
        $focusUserIds = $dailyService->getSubordinates($sfuserId);
        $data = $dailyService->getOthersDailyReportListEnable(
            $startDate,
            $endDate,
            $sfuserId,
            $focusUserIds['focus_users'],
            10000
        );

        if (empty($data) || empty($data['reports']) || empty($data['reports']['report_list'])) {
            info("[DailyReportAiEmailJob] task={$task->id} no report data, skip");
            return;
        }

        // 构建邮件内容（加密格式，由 oa-core 解密）
        $content = '';
        $no = 0;
        foreach ($data['reports']['report_list'] as $report) {
            $nickname = $report['data']['nickname'] ?? '';
            if (empty($nickname)) {
                continue;
            }
            $nickname = EncryptService::app()->markEncrString($nickname);
            $reportContent = EncryptService::app()->markEncrString($report['content']);
            ++$no;
            $content .= '<p><b>' . $no . '、 ' . $nickname . '</b></p>';
            $content .= '<div style="border:1px solid #eee;padding:8px;margin-bottom:12px;">' . $reportContent . '</div>';
        }

        $subject = "【{$startDate}】 {$task->name} - AI 分析";

        // 构建邮件参数（手动构建以支持 ai_analysis_config）
        $params = [
            'decrypt_config' => [
                'obj' => '$this',
                'decrypt_columns' => [],
                'partly_decrypt_columns' => ['content', 'subject'],
            ],
            'receivers' => [[
                'type' => 'token',
                'tokens' => [$sfuserToken],
                'filter' => 'emails',
                'filter_map' => ['emails' => $toEmails],
            ]],
            'content' => $content,
            'subject' => $subject,
            'ai_analysis_config' => [
                'system_prompt' => $task->system_prompt,
            ],
        ];

        info("[DailyReportAiEmailJob] task={$task->id} sending email to " . implode(',', $toEmails));
        CoreApiLib::sendRequest('master-api/mail/send-decr', $params);
        info("[DailyReportAiEmailJob] task={$task->id} email sent");
    }

    private function getDateRange(string $reportRange): array
    {
        $today = now()->toDateString();
        return match ($reportRange) {
            'today' => [$today, $today],
            'yesterday' => [now()->subDay()->toDateString(), now()->subDay()->toDateString()],
            default => [$today, $today],
        };
    }
}
```

### 2. Modify `D:\project\info-gitlab\oa\oa-server\app\Console\Kernel.php`

Add this line after the existing DailyReportJob line (line 56):
```php
$schedule->job(new \App\Jobs\Notification\DailyReportAiEmailJob())->everyMinute();
```

Find the line:
```
$schedule->job(new \App\Jobs\Notification\DailyReportJob())->dailyAt('08:48');
```
And add the new line right after it.

## Instructions
- Create the Job file using Write tool
- Read Kernel.php first, then use Edit tool to add the schedule line
- Do NOT modify any other files
- Do NOT create tests
- Do NOT commit

